    "description": "<p>The name “My First Skool” also embodies our ideals – a nurturing home for your child. In the same way that a seed only grows when it is planted in the right environment with the proper nutrients, My First Skool centres are staffed with trusted, passionate teachers whom your child can rely on to grow up strong, healthy, and adaptable. Once your children are older, they will be ready to face the world with confidence – much like a seedling sprouting fresh leaves from the ground.</p>",
